{"tid":1631623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬蹄露   單野都幾鬼吓","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:10:16.000Z","uid":269686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18911ab9c85846e97cff5eb69b2e732b59476743","tid":1631623,"uid":269686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"馬蹄露睇到有人毀爛中國銀行櫃員機的新聞片，看完發現一些特別的事，將短片的其中兩個時刻截圖了出來，圖片中用紅色橢圓形或長方形將一些在場但形跡可疑人士圈了出來。他們不似平常甚至勇武的示威者。長方形的似鄉黑人士，橢圓形的似popo。第25秒 (喂，你做乜野呀！) 及第30秒 (你咪郁手呀！) 那個喝停馬蹄露的語氣更似popo，你地覺得呢？<br />\n<br />\n有可能馬蹄露無意中見到扮示威者的鄉黑及popo在破壞中銀櫃員機，但馬又on9唔知係差佬做緊喬裝工作，因為馬係堅嬲，唔似做戲 (由於佢係藝人，所以用一般人既角度分柝佢，可能並不適用)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhr4yMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjhr4yMK.jpg&h=5e105b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eReRdML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeReRdML.jpg&h=2dd63fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191006/1570358642822/%e3%80%90%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95%e3%80%91%e6%92%90%e8%ad%a6%e9%a6%ac%e8%b9%84%e9%9c%b2%e8%a2%ab%e6%8c%87%e5%bd%b1%e4%ba%ba%e7%9b%b8-%e8%a1%80%e6%b5%81%e6%bb%bf%e9%9d%a2%e5%85%bc%e5%be%8c%e5%b0%be%e6%9e%95%e3%80%8c%e7%88%86%e7%bc%b8%e3%80%8d?fbclid=IwAR0LSTrsmRcK7sz2nLpUrPh-8-g9JnHlE-zoGP78OnvWXB6WdGJ_GdAdCxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191006%2F1570358642822%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2592%2590%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e8%25b9%2584%25e9%259c%25b2%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258c%2587%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%259b%25b8-%25e8%25a1%2580%25e6%25b5%2581%25e6%25bb%25bf%25e9%259d%25a2%25e5%2585%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e5%25b0%25be%25e6%259e%2595%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%2588%2586%25e7%25bc%25b8%25e3%2580%258d%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LSTrsmRcK7sz2nLpUrPh-8-g9JnHlE-zoGP78OnvWXB6W